Note on Sample Data:

The sample bearing vibration data in the `data/` directory is derived from 
MathWorks RollingElementBearingFaultDiagnosis-Data and is licensed under 
CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 (Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0).

For commercial use, please replace the sample data with your own vibration 
measurements or contact the original data provider for licensing.

Data Source: https://github.com/mathworks/RollingElementBearingFaultDiagnosis-Data
Data License: CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/)
